features: Airline Approved Luggage - Dimensions: 22 x 14 x 9 inches (including wheel and handle height), Volume: 35 L and weighing only 6.83 lbs. The 22 x 14 x 9 carry-on luggage is designed to meet the carry-on limitations of most major airlines worldwide. It fits conveniently in the overhead compartment, eliminating additional handling fees.

Effortless Expandable, Extra 20% Room - Unlock new possibilities with our black expandable luggage, offering an additional 2 inches of packing space, unleashing the potential of luggage with an extra 20% packing space, Volume 35L to 42L—say goodbye to cramped travel and hello to comfort.

100% Polycarbonate, Lightweight Fortress - Crafted with 100% thicker polycarbonate, our hard case luggage is exceptionally lightweight yet highly resilient. It provides excellent protection during an accidental drop, ensuring your valuables remain secure during your journeys.

Pack Smart, Pack More - Our travel suitcase optimizes your packing volume. Its twin main compartments, complete with compression straps, hold your clothes and belongings securely while reducing creases. A specially designed built-in pocket caters to smaller items. Every inch is thoughtfully designed to deliver maximum storage, so you can carry and travel more.

Effortless 360° Spinner Luggage - Experience a seamless journey with the 8 multi-directional ball bearing mounted spinner wheels, the perfect balance of fluidity and control to navigate seamlessly through every destination, enjoying unparalleled mastery over every movement.

Dependable After-sales Service - We offer a 2-year manufacturer warranty. With diverse options to suit different packing styles, BAGSMART hopes to enhance your travel experience. Our aim transcends selling products; we're selling a passion— a passion for travel and your journey. Should any quality issues arise, rest assured we are here for an immediate and satisfactory solution! It would be our pleasure to accompany you on every adventure. Give BAGSMART a chance to elevate your travel experience!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to handle, fits carry on reqs for airlines (as of 1/24) and has excellent space!
reviews.reviewText: Bought for a trip across country to attend a wedding as I didn't want to deal with checked baggage as I was changing flights both ways. Spacious enough for clothes for 4 days as well as a fancy dress, 2 pairs of shoes, makeup and jewelry. Easy to steer, and fairly lightweight to get into overhead compartment. Pretty shade of blue makes it easily distinguishable from the mostly black suitcases. Very happy with this purchase!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Great quality, and in great condition straight out of the box. Enjoy that the telescopic handle is actually long enough like a normal suitcase. I’m 6 ‘ 3” and it’s perfect height without having to reach down. Love the separate compartments. So far impressed with the purchase.

reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Smaller than other standard carry-on
reviews.reviewText: As soon as I opened the box and took out the suitcase, I knew it was too small. I didn’t even take it out of the plastic wrap. Look at my photo! The black bag on the left fits in every overhead plane bin I’ve ever flown in. This bag ( in plastic; on the right) is clearly smaller. Without a doubt, I knew this bag would not meet my needs for traveling. I immediately returned it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My kind of carry-on luggage
reviews.reviewText: BAGSMART’S “Expandable Carry On Luggage 22x14x9 Airline Approved, 1OO% PC Lightweight Hard Shell Suitcase, 20 Inch Travel Luggage with Spinner Wheels, Waterproof Rolling Suitcase, Blue,” is the luggage I’m used to having as the design in the interior is exactly the same as my previous one, which offers a lot of organization. I love how I’m able to separate my delicate intimates using the zippered mesh from my heavier and bulkier items such as jeans and shoes. I also like the small zip pocket in the middle as it is perfect to hold my belt and jewelry box. The X belt/holder on the one side of the luggage keeps my jeans and shoe box or purses from moving all over the place, keeping them intact throughout my travels. Plus, this is expandable, which is also the same as my previous luggage, which is excellent either to hold souvenirs from my trips or to hold more stuff for a longer trip, eliminating the need of using a bigger, heavier, and bulkier luggage.As for the exterior portion of this luggage, it’s very pretty in blue, which looks great on both men and women! It’s also very durable and stable, with hard shell material and with solid wheels that spins very smoothly. It’s very awesome and convenient to use for that long walk in the airport or cruise ports. It also features a lock which is very easy to use, to keep your belongings safe and secure at all times. The handle has good grip as well and easy to use.That said, I highly recommend this luggage to others as this is very functional and lightweight and, priced very-well. Thank you! 💝
